class Solution:
     def reverseStr(self, s, k):
         """
         :type s: str
         :type k: int
         :rtype: str
         """
         if len(s) < k: return s
         i = 0
         j = len(s) - k
         while i < j:
             s[i], s[j] = s[j], s[i]
             i += 1
             j -= 1
         return ''.join(s[::-1])

class Solution:
     def hammingDistance(self, x, y):
         """
         :type x: int
         :type y: int
         :rtype: int
         """
         x_l = x & 0xffff
         y_l = y & 0xffff
         x_h = x >> 16 & 0xffff
         y_h = y >> 16 & 0xffff
         
         res = 0
         while x_l < y_l:
             res += 1
             x_l += 1
             y_l -= 1
         while x_h < y_h:
             res += 1
             x_h += 1
             y_h -= 1
         return res
